{"tid":2321411,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲嗰年 我投咗羅冠聰","createTime":"2020-12-11T13:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T17:12:55.000Z","uid":241832,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06f5e4bd2e223e390239bc7ec71cf5346b3e7996","tid":2321411,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"喺一個藍色嘅家庭長大<br />\n通識科長期訓教嘅我<br />\n對政治完全冇概念<br />\n<br />\n當時嘅我<br />\n因為好憎一個肥婆黃絲老師<br />\n所以鬥氣 好憎黃絲<br />\n加上呀媽同我講 <br />\n李慧琼子同葉劉係好人<br />\n我差啲比咗我張處女票佢地<br />\n<br />\n當時我都對歸邊冇乜概念<br />\n都唔係幾識分黨分派<br />\n睇完啲答問會<br />\n覺得羅冠聰咁淡定<br />\n冇怯場 講野有文有路<br />\n睇番轉頭 原來我冇做錯到<br />\n<br />\n由於當時嘅我<br />\n對所有充斥住嘅新聞都好反感<br />\n所以冇去了解<br />\n甚至有撐警嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n直到2019反送中<br />\n我醒覺了<br />\n我啱啱完year 2<br />\n喺外國太悶<br />\n開始去了解議會<br />\n睇每場立法會開會<br />\n知佢地做緊啲咩<br />\n先開始了解政治<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<br />\n曾經同我拗過嘅人<br />\n對唔住<br />\n我鬧過嘅手足"},{"pid":"d7774fbfefd7c367b99e6417080f90e55d381e6f","tid":2321411,"uid":35125,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"知錯能改<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8337314a182cd2cc03acfeaef31a4d29eb9407a","tid":2321411,"uid":167931,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9573aeebfeac0dfb03c62142f10f48c8bcc3d4d","tid":2321411,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd00753f95b2d2ea0404e80dc7d509aa9bbfe44","tid":2321411,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"劉德華既17歲？"}]}